content:
You can use parameters, parameter mappings, and flow variables to send partner messaging conversation data to objects. This data gives agents more context for who they’re messaging with.

Create a Support Reason dropdown menu, and then route the customer’s input to the Messaging Session object.

This change applies to Partner Messaging. View required editions.

Consult your partner messaging documentation for setup steps.
title: Route Data to Objects in Partner Messaging (Beta)
